# Votely project rules

Read `AGENTS.md` at repo root before making changes.

- Stack: Vue 3 Composition API, Vite, Tailwind (`darkMode: class`).
- Do not edit `raw_resource/` unless explicitly asked.
- Preserve localStorage keys in `src/constants/storage.js`.
- UI copy in Vietnamese.
- Run `npm run build` after non-trivial changes.
